Item.ВыполнениеКода_ПодсказкаКонтекстКлиентаРасширеннаяПодсказка.Title=Initially the <b>&AtClient</> code runs, from which you can already invoke execution <b>&AtServer </>via method <b>ExecuteCodeAtServer(TextAtServer, AdditionalParameters);</>\n\n<b><colorstyle -3>Available variables\:</></>\n<colorstyle -3> </><u><colorstyle -3>CurrentForm</></><colorstyle -3>   </><colorstyle -3>- the selected open form;</>\n<colorstyle -3> </><u><colorstyle -3>TextAtServer</></><b><colorstyle -3>   </></><colorstyle -3>- the text of the code that runs on the  server</>\n<colorstyle -3> </><u><colorstyle -3>AdditionalParameters</></><b><colorstyle -3> </></><colorstyle -3>- a structure for exchanging data between  client and server</>\n\n<b><colorstyle -3>Available  methods\:</></>\n<colorstyle -3> </><u><colorstyle -3>ExecuteCodeAtServer(TextAtServer, AdditionalParameters);</></>\n\n\n\n
Item.ВыполнениеКода_ПодсказкаКонтекстСервераРасширеннаяПодсказка.Title=The code runs in the server context but cannot access the form. Required for retrieving values, for example, from queries.\n\n<b>Available variables\:</>\n<u>AdditionalParameters </>-  a structure for exchanging data between client and server
