Item.Команда_ПроверитьНаличиеРеквизитаРасширеннаяПодсказка.Title=Checks for attribute presence in the form for subsequent interactive editing.\n\nSince the platform has no way to retrieve the attribute list of another open form, this tool implements a mechanism for searching attributes. Not all attributes can be detected automatically, however, presence can be checked manually.\n\nThe tool settings also allow specifying a list of attribute names whose presence will be automatically checked in every open form.
