Item.ОткрытыеФормыРеквизитыРасширеннаяПодсказка.Title=Contains the attributes tree of the selected form.\n\nYou can change values of attributes and form tables.\n\nDue to platform limitations, you cannot retrieve the attribute list of another open form. This tool implements form "scanning" by built-in templates. Presence of attributes that could not be detected can be verified manually by entering the attribute name in the field at the bottom of the table.\n\nThe tool settings also allow specifying a list of attribute names whose presence will be automatically checked in every open form.
Item.ОткрытыеФормыСвойстваРасширеннаяПодсказка.Title=List of form properties with the ability to set values.\n\nThe list is refreshed via the corresponding context menu item (or by pressing F5).\nThe properties list contains <u>AutoTitle</>, <u>Enabled</>,  <u>Title</>, <u>Modified</>, <u>ReadOnly</>\n\nIt is possible to set the value of any arbitrary form property in the  "<u>Arbitrary set</>" item
Item.ОткрытыеФормыУникальныйИдентификаторРасширеннаяПодсказка.Title=Unique identifier of the form. All processing methods operate with it when identifying the form.
Item.ОткрытыеФормыЭлементыКонтекстноеМенюГруппа1.Title=Display
Item.ОткрытыеФормыЭлементыПоложениеЗаголовка.Title=Position
Item.ОткрытыеФормыЭлементыРасширеннаяПодсказка.Title=Contains the items tree of the selected form.\n\nYou can change properties\: <u>Visibility</>, <u>ReadOnly</>,  <u>Enabled</>.\n\nDouble-clicking an item activates the selected form with positioning on the selected item.\n\nThe tree is refreshed via the corresponding context menu item (or by pressing F5).\n\n
